      <title>西非的气候危机使巧克力变得更加昂贵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2023-12-01/chocolate-gets-pricier-as-cocoa-beans-in-west-africa-rot-from-climate-crisis</link>
